  "detailed_description": "<h1>Add to wishlists now!</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034020/extras/f29a07b9c20caf66ed7a88e27bb93767.poster.avif?t=1710370857\" width=616 height=94 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034020/extras/f29a07b9c20caf66ed7a88e27bb93767.webm?t=1710370857\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034020/extras/c4fe545ecc874bef8f2f680039f97624.avif?t=1710370857\" width=600 height=315 /></span><br><br>Dive into this exciting and colorful adventure! Help Corbid overcome the challenging mazes and secure his place as champion. Get ready to have fun as you embark on this colorful and exciting mission, where you'll have to use your dexterity and skills to solve the intricate puzzles in the huge gardens.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034020/extras/ba9da1371af11f163b8d83aa2cc98d0b.poster.avif?t=1710370857\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034020/extras/ba9da1371af11f163b8d83aa2cc98d0b.webm?t=1710370857\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034020/extras/ba9da1371af11f163b8d83aa2cc98d0b.mp4?t=1710370857\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034020/extras/5eae2edc980e9399cd00c7606adc17ea.avif?t=1710370857\" width=600 height=368 /></span><br>The gardens are full of fun riddles and puzzles in which you will have to do your best to advance. Use all your resources, feel the speed and the frenzy of the jumps to get as far as you can. Also, let yourself be advised by different allies and even help some of them to unlock new areas.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034020/extras/37c29c45e45e76b1585cde1c59f749fd.poster.avif?t=1710370857\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034020/extras/37c29c45e45e76b1585cde1c59f749fd.webm?t=1710370857\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034020/extras/37c29c45e45e76b1585cde1c59f749fd.mp4?t=1710370857\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034020/extras/4d169a848524f430af90fccd69aba5df.avif?t=1710370857\" width=600 height=368 /></span><br>Find adventure companions on your journey to help you complete fun scenarios and become more effective against dangers. Combine skills to achieve unique moves and solve more complex puzzles. Above all, make friends!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034020/extras/dd30b8a617bfba6309b1c7942caca656.poster.avif?t=1710370857\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034020/extras/dd30b8a617bfba6309b1c7942caca656.webm?t=1710370857\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034020/extras/dd30b8a617bfba6309b1c7942caca656.mp4?t=1710370857\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034020/extras/5e4418e5b0b514f01bcd6ac556e89016.avif?t=1710370857\" width=600 height=368 /></span><br><br>Get ready to fight in thrilling battles against terrifying final bosses. Use Corbid's skills to find the enemies' weaknesses and defeat them in a battle that will keep you on the edge of your seat - don't give up, stay focused and secure victory against these formidable opponents!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034020/extras/e7a8bd279c332f3a975f2f8200c3cc64.poster.avif?t=1710370857\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034020/extras/e7a8bd279c332f3a975f2f8200c3cc64.webm?t=1710370857\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034020/extras/e7a8bd279c332f3a975f2f8200c3cc64.mp4?t=1710370857\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034020/extras/3485378d3d1614ad9250959cd74da23b.avif?t=1710370857\" width=600 height=368 /></span><br><br>Embark on an adventure through lush and vibrant worlds filled with creatures of every color imaginable. Dive into the mysteries hidden in the vast gardens and unravel the secrets they hold. Enjoy a wonderful journey where the magic of color will surprise you around every corner.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034020/extras/8b905071a12b2ad1c2ce7bc0f3993fbc.poster.avif?t=1710370857\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034020/extras/8b905071a12b2ad1c2ce7bc0f3993fbc.webm?t=1710370857\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034020/extras/8b905071a12b2ad1c2ce7bc0f3993fbc.mp4?t=1710370857\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
